Subject: [PATCH 11/16] feat(pronunciation): "Hear it" exemplar button +
 target-word TTS

- "Hear it" button plays a jingo-tts model pronunciation of the target word
  before the learner records; config-gated by PRONUNCIATION_TTS_URL (empty=hidden).
- spokenText(): send only the target word to TTS (strip the "Escucha y repite:"
  instruction and the "-- translation").
- Record button relabeled "Speak it" / "Speak again".
- Wiring: myconfig.pronunciation_tts_url -> window.config.pronunciationTtsUrl ->
  <pronunciation-question :tts-url>. Works in student view and instructor preview.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_01CRePd9rbvtz6UqFuuYMi9U
